        <num>CC 1314</num>
        <heading>1314.  Defense of suits by tutors, curators and emancipated minors</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1314.  Defense of suits by tutors, curators and emancipated minors.
But the authorization of the judge is not necessary to enable tutors or curators of minors or persons interdicted or minors emancipated, to answer suits for partition brought against them.</p>
        </content>
